erved roughly proportionally to their weights.", "Creatives are served exactly in sequential order, also known as Storyboarding." ] }, "frequencyCap": { "items": { "$ref": "FrequencyCap" }, "type": "array", "readOnly": true, "description": "Output only. Specifies any frequency caps. Cannot be filtered within ListDealsRequest." } } }, "CancelNegotiationRequest": { "type": "object", "description": "Request to cancel an ongoing negotiation.", "id": "CancelNegotiationRequest", "properties": {} }, "ListDealsResponse": { "description": "Response message for listing deals in a proposal.", "type": "object", "id": "ListDealsResponse", "properties": { "deals": { "type": "array", "description": "The list of deals.", "items": { "$ref": "Deal" } }, "nextPageToken": { "type": "string", "description": "Token to fetch the next page of results." } } }, "CriteriaTargeting": { "id": "CriteriaTargeting", "type": "object", "description": "Generic targeting used for targeting dimensions that contains a list of included and excluded numeric IDs. This cannot be filtered using list filter syntax.", "properties": { "excludedCriteriaIds": { "description": "A list of numeric IDs to be excluded.", "items": { "type": "string", "format": "int64" }, "type": "array" }, "targetedCriteriaIds": { "items": { "format": "int64", "type": "string" }, "type": "array", "description": "A list of numeric IDs to be included." } } }, "MarketplaceTargeting": { "properties": { "videoTargeting": { "readOnly": true, "description": "Output only. Video targeting information.", "$ref": "VideoTargeting" }, "daypartTargeting": { "$ref": "DayPartTargeting", "description": "Daypart targeting information." }, "inventorySizeTargeting": { "$ref": "InventorySizeTargeting", "readOnly": true, "description": "Output only. Inventory sizes to be included/excluded." }, "placementTargeting": { "readOnly": true, "description": "Output only. Placement targeting information, for example, URL, mobile applications.", "$ref": "PlacementTar